Description: CLI tool for synchronizing markdown documentation with Jira
 A production-grade CLI tool for synchronizing markdown documentation
 with Jira issue tracking system.
 .
 Features:
  - Full Epic Sync - Sync user stories, subtasks, descriptions, and comments
  - Markdown-Native - Write epic documentation in markdown
  - Smart Matching - Fuzzy title matching between markdown and Jira issues
  - Safe by Default - Dry-run mode, confirmations, and detailed previews
  - Command Pattern - Undo-capable operations with full audit trail
  - Plugin System - Extensible architecture for custom integrations

